instruction: Make a list of indoor activities to keep kids entertained.
output:
Indoor activities to keep kids entertained include: 
-Board games 
-Jigsaw puzzles 
-Playing dress-up 
-Indoor camping 
-Making crafts 
-Building a fort 
-Playing charades 
-Indoor scavenger hunt 
-Cooking and baking 
-Creating an obstacle course 
-Making a movie 
-Have a dance party 
-Playing pretend 
-Reading books
